Photorealistic style: A tense boardroom scene captured from a dramatic low angle, showing two hands hovering over opposite ends of a vintage brass balance scale. On one side sits a stack of crisp currency bills, on the other a tangled mass of colorful ethernet cables and circuit boards. The scale tips precariously toward the technology side. Dramatic side lighting casts long shadows across a polished mahogany table surface, creating a chiaroscuro effect. In the soft-focus background, tall windows reveal a stormy sky with dark clouds gathering. The mood is contemplative and weighted with consequence, emphasizing the delicate equilibrium between financial investment and technical uncertainty. Shallow depth of field keeps attention on the pivoting scale mechanism, its brass patina catching golden light.
